questionSubtextContent: How often do you find yourself feeling anxious or uneasy? Do you worry about the future, past mistakes, or everyday challenges?
Do you find it easy to connect with and build relationships with new people? Are you comfortable in social situations?
Do you enjoy daydreaming or fantasizing about things? Are you able to think creatively and come up with new ideas?
Do you generally believe in the honesty and integrity of others? Are you willing to trust people with your secrets or personal information?
Are you organized and efficient in completing tasks? Do you meet deadlines and achieve your goals?
Do you often feel overwhelmed by stress or find it hard to stay calm in challenging situations?

questionHeadingContent: Enjoy being the center of attention
questionSubtextContent: Do you feel comfortable when all eyes are on you? Do you enjoy taking the lead in social settings?
Do you enjoy stepping out of your comfort zone and trying unfamiliar activities or ideas?
Do you empathize with people when they are going through tough times? Are you compassionate and supportive?
Do you prefer to have a regular schedule and plan your activities in advance? Do you dislike disruptions to your routine?
